Class IValueMatchCustomiser

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.ac.manchester.cs.mekon.store.disk.IValueMatchCustomiser

  • public class IValueMatchCustomiser
extends java.lang.Object
    Provides customised query matching for a particular value-type, via a specific ICustomValueMatcher, together with a particular set of applicable slot-types.
